{
  "stem": "719.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I figured-- also, if she would have left my father, she would have gone with me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because I, in my camp-- like I said, this wasn't an extermination.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There were mothers and daughters working together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "As long as you did what-- what the factory work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I remember she like waved to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She didn't leave my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They both went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The only thing I would like to know-- I never will-- if they suffered long.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[SOBBING] If they took the-- If they burned them, or if they gassed them, or whatever, how long they suffered.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "If they had a-- a fast-- it always-- this one thing always stings.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But you know, when I was liberated, I wasn't as emotional as-- as I got older.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Everybody was an orphan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Everybody was liberated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We were all young people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We were all starting a new life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't a novelty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I wasn't the only one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I Wasn't an orphan, here I am alone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We were hundreds of us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We came all back together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I didn't think about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I didn't think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I didn't even mourn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I didn't mourn enough because I didn't think about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I convinced myself, they're not dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It can't be.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Can't be.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's the way I-- I lived till 1943.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in 1944, when the rumors spread that the Germans came back from Russia defeated, that the Allies started to approach, we used to go, come on, already.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When are you going to come?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were praying that the Allies get into the war and come.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the beginning, '45, when Auschwitz was already liberated, we heard rumors that male camps are being evacuated.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we saw transports of skeletons walking past.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we weren't allowed-- we couldn't-- we couldn't even approach.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
